  <Content>Knighthood

For the first time in Temuair, Loures is granting the title of Knighthood to select Aislings, a position that was once held by only Mundanes.  Knights are keepers of the peace, resolving problems between Aislings. They have a direct line of communication with the Mundanes. They deal with both Aisling law and Mundane law.  Knights do not enforce any form of punishment. They are mediators, if a problem cannot be solved with town officials or Rangers then they can report to the Mundanes using the Knight Board. 

Candidacy
