The first ten Knights will be selected by the Mundanes. Knights thereafter will be selected by current Knights based on the comments on the candidacy board.

Knights will be given class specific armor and uniform. ((Armors were made exclusively for Dark Ages!!))

Knights can lose their Knighthood if they severely violate Aisling or Mundane Law and/or behave in a manner that is inappropriate of a Knight.

Duty
The main duty of a Knight is to help resolve problems between Aislings, community problems.  Knights may also report other issues such as corrupt political officials, abusers, harassers, problem peasants,etc. ((As wells as bugs))

